gov.nih.nlm.meme.common
Class AUI

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.common.AUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable, Identifier, Rankable
public class AUI
extends Object
implements Identifier

Represents a unique identifier for an atom. This roughly corresponds to a SUI, versionless source, term-type, and a code. It is an implementation of Identifier because it is a kind of identifier but generally, its Rank is not useful.

Author:
MEME Group
